\c 43
\p
\v 1 Zvino nzara yakange iri huru munyika iyoyo.
\v 2 Zvino vakati vapedza zviyo, zvavakange vabva nazvo Egipita, baba vavo vakati kwavari, Dzokai, endaizve mutitengere zvokudya zvishoma.
\p
\v 3 Judha akataura navo, akati, Murume uya akatinyevera kwazvo, akati, Hamungatongooni chiso changu, kana munin'ina wenyu asati anemi.
\v 4 Kana mukatuma munin'ina wedu nesu, tichaburuka, kundotenga zvokudya;
\v 5 asi kana musingamutumi, hatingaburuki; nekuti murume uya akati kwatiri, Hamungaoni chiso changu, kana munin'ina wenyu asati anemi.
\p
\v 6 Israeri akati, Makandiitireiko zvakaipa zvakadai, zvamakaudza murume uya kuti munomunin'ina?
\v 7 Ivo vakati, Murume uya akatibvunzisisa pamusoro pedu, napamusoro pehama dzedu, akati, Baba venyu vapenyu here? Mune munin'ina here? Tikamupindura namashoko aya; taigoziva here kuti achati, Burukai nomunin'ina wenyu?
\p
\v 8 Zvino Judha akati kuna Israeri, baba vake, Tumai henyu mukomana neni, tisimuke, tiende, tirarame, tirege kufa, isu nemi, navana vedu.
\v 9 Ini ndichava rubatso rwake; mungamureva paruoko rwangu; kana ndikasauya naye, ndikamuisa pamberi penyu, ini ndichava nemhosva kwamuri nokusingaperi.
\v 10 Nokuti dai tisina kunonoka, zvirokwazvo, tingadai tadzoka zvino rwechipiri.
\p
\v 11 Ipapo Israeri, baba vavo, akati kwavari, Kana zvakadaro, itai chinhu ichi; torai michero yakanaka yenyika mumidziyo yenyu, muburuke nechipo kumunhu uyo, chebhasami shomanana, nouchi ushomanana, nezvinonhuhwira, nemura, nemichero yomuti wepisitakio, namaamanda;
\v 12 mutore mari yakapamhidzwa kaviri mumaoko enyu, neiya mari yakange yadzoserwa mumiromo yehomwe dzenyu, muende makaibata mumaoko enyu; zvimwe vakakanganisa.
\v 13 Nomunin'ina wenyu mumutorei, musimuke, mudzokere kumurume uyo;
\v 14 Mwari Wemasimbaose ngaakupei nyasha pamberi pomurume uyo, akusunungurirei umwe munin'ina wenyu naBhenjaminiwo. Kana ndatorerwa vana vangu, ndatorerwa hangu.
\p
\v 15 Zvino varume vakatora chipo ichocho, vakabata mumaoko avo mari yakapamhidzwa kaviri, naBhenjamini, vakasimuka, vakaburukira Egipita, vakandomira pamberi paJosefa.
\v 16 Zvino Josefa akati achiona Bhenjamini anavo, akati kumutariri weimba yake, Uya navarume mumba, ubaye, ugadzire; nokuti varume ava vachadya neni masikati.
\v 17 Murume uyo akaita sezvaakaudzwa naJosefa; murume uyo akaisa varume avo mumba maJosefa.
\p
\v 18 Varume vakatya, zvavakaiswa mumba maJosefa, vakati, Tinoiswamo nokuda kwemari yakadzoserwa muhomwe dzedu panguva yokutanga, kuti atsvake mhosva kwatiri, atibate, nokutiita varanda vake, achitorawo madhongi edu.
\v 19 Ipapo vakaswedera kumutariri weimba yaJosefa, vakataura naye pamusuwo weimba;
\v 20 vakati, Haiwa, ishe wedu, zvirokwazvo panguva yokutanga takaburuka kuzotenga zvokudya;
\v 21 tikati tichisvika patakarara usiku, tikasunungura homwe dzedu, onei mari yomumwe neumwe iri mumuromo wehomwe yake, mari yedu yose sezvayakayerwa; zvino tadzoka nayo pamaoko edu.
\v 22 Zvino taburuka tiine imwe marizve mumaoko edu kuti titenge zvokudya nayo; hatizivi kuti mari yedu yakaiswa muhomwe dzedu nani?
\p
\v 23 Iye akati, Farai henyu, musatya; Mwari wenyu, Mwari wababa venyu, akakupai fuma muhomwe dzenyu; mari yenyu yakasvika kwandiri. Akavabudisira Simioni.
\p
\v 24 Murume uyo akaisa varume avo muimba yaJosefa, akavapa mvura, vakashambidza tsoka dzavo, akapawo mbongoro dzavo zvokudya.
\v 25 Vakagadzira chipo kusvikira kuuya kwaJosefa masikati, nekuti vakange vanzwa kuti vachadya zvokudya ipapo.
\v 26 Josefa akati asvika kumba, vakapinda mumba nechipo chakange chiri mumaoko avo, vakakotamira pasi pamberi pake.
\v 27 Iye akavabvunza mufaro wavo, akati, Baba venyu vakafara here, uya mutana wamaireva? Vachiri vapenyu here?
\p
\v 28 Ivo vakati, Muranda wenyu, baba vedu, vakafara havo, vachiri vapenyu. Vakakotama, vakanamata.
\p
\v 29 Iye akasimudza meso ake, akaona Bhenjamini, munin'ina wake, mwanakomana wamai vake, akati, Ndiye here munin'ina wenyu muduku worugotwe, wamakandiudza? Akati, Mwari ngaave nenyasha newe, mwana wangu.
\v 30 Zvino Josefa akakurumidza, nekuti moyo wake wakachema munin'ina wake, akatsvaka paangachema; akapinda muimba yake yomukati, akachemapo.
\v 31 Akazoshambidza chiso chake, akabudazve, akazvidzora akati, Pakurai zvokudya.
\v 32 Vakamupakurira iye oga, naivo vega, navaEgipita havana kutenderwa kudya navaHebheru, nekuti zvinonyangadza kuna vaEgipita.
\v 33 Vakagara pamberi pake, wedangwe paudangwe hwake, nomuduku kuna vose pauduku hwake; varume vakatarirana, vakashamiswa.
\v 34 Akavagovera zvokudya zvakange zviri pamberi pake, asi mugove waBhenjamini wakaenzana nowavashanu vavo. Vakanwa , vakafara naye.
